# Financial Risk Capital Adequacy Policy Liability Gross Aggregate Amount

## identifier
de5393

## type
float

## definition
Report the aggregated value of the capital adequacy liability for all related product groups, as calculated by the capital adequacy standard, gross of reinsurance. These are the guaranteed liabilities under life insurance policies on the basis of assumptions which are more conservative (anticipate a more adverse experience) than best estimate and solvency assumptions.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.CapitalAdequacy.PolicyLiabilityGrossAggregate.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.05
- period=instant
